#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmix; supports several platforms and sound drivers."
msgstr "يدعم مازج.ك منصات ومشغلات صوت عدة."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have both ALSA and Open Sound System drivers installed, &kmix; will "
"use the ALSA driver."
msgstr "إن ثُبّت مشغلا ALSA و Open Sound System معًا، سيستخدم مازج.ك مشغل ALSA."

